title: Say Cheese/Finders Keepers/A Frog in Caillou's Throat/Caillou the Great
description: Caillou tries his hand at being family photographer and discovers it can be a pretty tricky job./Caillou and Leo can't find Caillou's airplane anywhere but their hunt through the house turns up all sorts of other lost items./After getting caught in the rain, Caillou loses his voice./Caillou is invited to Leo's birthday party and is overjoyed when he discovers there will be a magician present.

title: The Little Bird/Lights Out/Caillou's Check Up/Calling Dr. Caillou
description: Caillou and Sarah find a baby bird that fell from its nest./A winter storm knocks the power out at Caillou's home./It's time for Caillou's visit to the dentist./Caillou is really looking forward to a special day at work with Dad.

title: Caillou and the Big Slide/Caillou the Sailor/Caillou and the Creepy Crawlies
description: The playschool is going swimming, and it's Caillou's very first time on a water slide./Mommy and Daddy are going out to a party and Caillou is excited to hear that Grandpa is coming to babysit./Rosie doesn't like bugs - she thinks they're icky!

title: Something for Everyone/Skating Lessons/Caillou Becomes a Waiter/Sticking to It!/New Clothes
description: When the park is closed for the day, Caillou's friends come over to his house to play./When Mom drives Sarah to her skating lesson, Caillou decides he wants to take skating lessons too!/When Mom and Dad are getting ready to go out to a restaurant, Caillou doesn't understand why he can't go too!/When Caillou accidentally breaks one of his toys because his room is a mess, Mom suggests a way to make cleaning up fun./When Caillou dresses himself, he learns it's okay to change from your favorite shorts when you find out it's cold outside.

title: Sunday Brunch/Caillou to the Rescue/Caillou's Top Bunk/Recipe For Fun
description: Caillou, Dad and Rosie take Mom out for Sunday brunch to celebrate Mother's Day./Gilbert gets caught up a tree, and to Caillou's delight a fire truck full of firefighters has to be called in to rescue him./Caillou and Rosie get to spend the night at Grandma and Grandpa's house./Dad drives Caillou to Grandma's for the day.

title: One, Two, Boom!/Out of the Woods/House Paint/Caillou's Thanksgiving
description: Caillou is awoken by a thunderstorm./Caillou spends the day with Miss Martin, Clementine and Leo on a nature hike through the woods./When Caillou sees Dad painting the house he wants to join in on the fun./It's a beautiful fall day and Caillou wants to spend the entire day outside playing in the leaves.

title: Caillou Goes Shopping/Caillou Goes Apple Picking/Caillou's Halloween Costume
description: Caillou's crayons are all worn down or broken, so Mommy suggests a trip to the store for some new ones./Caillou's playschool is on a special field trip to an apple orchard./Halloween is coming and it's time to pick out a costume to wear.

title: Caillou Beats the Heat/Back Seat Driver/Lost and Found/Holiday Magic
description: It's hot and steamy and Mom won't let Caillou go to the public pool./Caillou, Dad and Rosie are in the car on their way to meet Mom./When Dad and Caillou find a scruffy dog that appears to be lost they bring it home./Caillou and his family pay a visit to Santa and go Christmas tree shopping all in the same day.

title: Super Caillou!/Trip on the Subway/Caillou's Race/As Good as New/I, Robot
description: Caillou just loves his Superbear storybook./Caillou learns to deal with a change in plans when Daddy has to use the car./Caillou is playing a board game with Mom and he gets a little upset./Caillou learns about 'recycling' -- literally!/ When Sarah shows Caillou and Leo her new remote controlled robot, the boys get a great idea to be robots too!

title: The Beach/New Shoes/Snowman/Clown/Special Friend
description: Caillou and his family are at the beach./Caillou gets a new pair of shoes./Caillou wants to make a snowman./Caillou is going to a parade with horses, drummers and clowns./Caillou's having fun with his friend.

title: Backyard Zoo/Caillou's Scavenger Hunt/Too Many Cooks/The Berry Patch
description: Caillou and Clementine and Leo make their own zoo in the backyard./When Julie comes over to babysit she announces that she's brought along a really fun game./Caillou's babysitter is late./Caillou spends a day strawberry picking.

title: Elephants!/Caillou and the Sheep/Caillou and the Puppies/The Duck Family/Clementine's New Pet
description: When Mom, Rosie and Caillou go to the zoo, Caillou can't wait to see the elephants./Grandma takes Caillou on a special visit to a sheep farm./Caillou and Dad go over to Mr. Hinkle's house to help him build a dog house./While Caillou and his family are on a picnic at the park, his beach ball accidentally rolls into a pond./When Mom takes Caillou to Clementine's to see her new pet, she won't tell Caillou what kind of animal it is.

title: Captain Caillou/The Loudest Noise/Caillou's First Wedding
description: Grandpa's got a surprise for Caillou on their trip to the park - it's a remote control sailboat!/Mommy sends Caillou to play outside because he's making too much noise and it's Rosie's nap time./Daddy and Mommy's friend Jonas is getting married.

title: Caillou's Suitcase/Try, Try Again/The New Leaf/Happy New Year
description: Caillou's very excited about a family trip and decides to pack his own suitcase./Caillou has trouble learning to tie his shoelaces./Caillou, Grandpa and Dad go for a special hike in the woods./Caillou celebrates Chinese New Year.

title: Big Kick/Jungle Explorer/The Caillou Show/Loves Halloween/Picnic
description: André comes to visit./Caillou's friend Sarah has a magnifying glass./There's a special event at Caillou's daycare./It's trick-or-treat time. Caillou's dressed as an astronaut./Caillou invites Leo to go on a family picnic.

title: Caillou Goes to the Car Wash/Far Away Home/All You Can Eat/Caillou Stays Up Late
description: Caillou, Dad and Rosie take the car to the car wash./Caillou uses his imagination to turn the house into the setting for a desert expedition./Caillou and Mom are joining Clementine and her mom for a picnic./Caillou finds out his parents are having a grown-up party.

title: Makes Cookies/Not Afraid Anymore/Hates Vegetables/All Alone/Tidies His Toys
description: Caillou is having fun being noisy./Caillou is afraid of Mr. Hinkle, the kind neighbor./Caillou really hates vegetables./Mom is very busy with chores and doesn't have time to play with Caillou./Caillou has left his toys all over the place.

title: Dancing at Grandma's/Mystery Valentine/Play Ball!/Dogsled Ahead!
description: It is a rainy day and Caillou is disappointed because he will not be able to go play at the park with Grandma./It's Valentine's day and Caillou is invited to a Valentine's party at his best friend Leo's house./When Dad's baseball team, the Tigers, are playing a game at the park, Caillou, Rosie and Mom go to cheer him on./Caillou and his family are heading to the tobogganing hill!

title: Downhill From Here/Next Stop Fun/Under Sail/Farmer Caillou
description: Mom, an avid skier, takes Caillou downhill skiing while Dad and Rosie sit in the cozy chalet and watch./Caillou is very excited when the family takes a trip across country by train./Caillou finds an old toy sailing boat./Mr. Hinkle invites Caillou to visit his sister's farm.

title: Magnet Madness/Caillou the Dinosaur Hunter/Caillou the Astronaut
description: Caillou is playing with the fridge magnets and learns lots of things about them./The whole family goes on a trip to the natural history museum to look at the dinosaurs./Caillou wants to play with both his friends Clementine and Xavier at the playschool playground.

title: Star Light, Star Bright/All in a Day's Work/The Cat's Meow/Caillou in Space
description: Caillou and the family are at Grandma & Grandpa's for an evening corn roast./The house wakes up late, and that means it's a mad rush to get off to work and off to childcare./It's time for Gilbert's annual visit to the Vet./When Caillou plays astronauts with Leo he upsets Rosie.

title: Caillou's Cricket/Dog Dilemma/The Spider Issue
description: Caillou inadvertently brings a cricket in the house./When Sarah gets a new dog, Caillou is actually a little jealous./Caillou feels afraid of real spiders.

title: What's Ringette?/Rainy Day at the Beach/Caillou Climbs
description: Caillou and Leo want to play hockey./Caillou and his family are supposed to be enjoying a nice day./Mommy takes Caillou and Clementine to an indoor rock climbing wall.

title: Daycare/Joins the Circus/Afraid of the Dark/Friends/Visits the Doctor
description: It's Caillou's first day at daycare and he doesn't want to go./Caillou gets dressed all by himself./Caillou can't get to sleep./Caillou is talking to Grandma. She's surprised./Caillou has an ear infection.

title: A Present for Mommy/Caillou the Chef/Caillou the Painter
description: Mommy's having a bad day - first she can't find her car keys, then she and Caillou have to shovel the car out, and then the car won't start!/Jeffrey and Jason are coming over for dinner - it's a make-your-own pizza party!/Caillou's got a brand new painting shirt and decides to paint something for Grandma.

title: Disappearing Carrots/Caillou Marches On/Who's Mooing/Follow That Sound!/The Music Box!
description: When a white rabbit eats a bunch of carrots set aside for a picnic lunch, Caillou and Rosie go looking him./When Caillou visits Clementine, he is impressed to see Billy practicing on a tuba./Caillou and his family are leaving for a picnic in the country but the ride feels very long for Caillou./On a winter evening, a strange sound grabs Caillou's attention./Caillou goes up to the attic with Mom and finds a box containing a teddy bear and a music box.

title: Big Brother/Hiding Place/Rainy Day/Rakes the Leaves/Goes Shopping
description: Caillou remembers when he first met his sister./Caillou is at his Grandparents' house./It's a rainy day and Caillou wants to jump in all the puddles./Caillou and Rosie have so much fun playing in the leaves./Caillou is looking forward to making a snowman.

title: Caillou's Favorite Plate/Fun in the Mud/All Aboard!/I Scream for Ice Cream/Gilbert's House
description: Grandma has given Caillou a special spaceship plate./It's raining outside but there is no stopping Caillou!/After finding a photograph of a four-year-old Dad with a model train set, Caillou and Dad decide to look for it./When Caillou spots a dog house outside he gets the idea that Gilbert might like a house of his own./Caillou, Rosie and Mom are having fun at the park when the ice-cream man comes around.

title: Caillou the Librarian/Caillou the Bookworm/Caillou the Storyteller
description: Caillou is excited about showing Rosie the ropes when they visit the library./Returning home from the library Caillou is very eager to sit down and enjoy his pirate book./It's a rainy day at playschool and the children can't go outside.

title: Pumpkin Patch Kid/Caillou's Got Rhythm/Do It Myself/Caillou's Big Sale
description: Grandpa and Caillou go for a visit to a pumpkin patch./During a visit to the park with Grandma, Caillou and Rosie see some musicians playing outside./After Caillou sees what Clementine is giving her Dad for Father's Day, he wants to give his Daddy something just as special./Caillou's very excited about the neighborhood rummage sales.

title: Caillou Roller Skates/Say Lettuce!/Caillou Tries to Whistle
description: Caillou wants to learn how to roller skate./Caillou wants to take a picture of a bunny rabbit in Grandma's garden./ Clementine can whistle, and Caillou can't!

title: Caillou's Teddy Shirt/Caillou Meets Robbie/The Pinata/Caillou's Promise
description: Caillou's favorite shirt has teddy bears on it./Caillou introduces himself to another little boy at the park./Caillou can't wait for the mailman to deliver his invitation to his friend Xavier's party./Caillou learns about keeping promises.

title: Caillou the Patient/Caillou the Police Officer/Grandpa's Friend
description: While pretending to be a jet pilot Caillou falls down and scrapes his knees./When the traffic lights near school stop working a policeman comes to direct traffic./Grandpa takes Caillou to the park one fine day to meet his friend George.

title: Coins/Canoe Trip/The Bulldozer/The Firefighter/The Timekeeper
description: Caillou accompanies Mom to the grocery store./When Caillou, Grandpa and Daddy go on a canoe trip, Caillou gets to see some wild animals./On an autumn day, Caillou and his Mommy take a walk and pass by a construction site./When Dad's burning toasts trigger the fire alarm, he decides it is the perfect opportunity to practice a fire drill./Caillou and his Mommy are finishing preparing a picnic lunch.

title: Caillou Plays the Drums/Caillou's Marching Band/Caillou Sings
description: Clementine's big brother Billy has a new drum set and is having lots of fun playing as loud as he can./Caillou and his friends are very excited when a real marching band goes by the playschool./The playschool is having a talent show and Caillou wants to sing a song.

title: Surprise Party/Caillou's Bad Dream/Caillou Computes/Caillou's Big Discovery
description: Caillou helps Grandma put together a belated surprise party./After a scary nightmare, Caillou doesn't want to sleep in his own bed./Caillou's very excited when Dad brings home a computer./While playing dinosaurs in the backyard, Caillou and Leo dig up a fish fossil rock.

title: Caillou's Surprise/A Surprise for Miss Martin/A Surprise Sleepover
description: When Caillou accidentally breaks Mommy's favorite cup, Grandma suggests they make her a new one./When Caillou finds out that Miss Martin's birthday is coming up, he wants to do something very special for her./Sarah is playing at Caillou's house when a sudden rainstorm causes a power outage.

title: Comic Caper!/Hide and Seek/Caillou's Clouds/Caillou Cleans Up
description: Caillou and Dad are settling down for their favorite weekend ritual of "reading" the paper./Caillou can't seem to play quietly in his room without Rosie interrupting./Caillou, Mom and Rosie go to the park for a picnic and bring a kite./Mom and Dad are busy with spring cleaning and Caillou wants to help.

title: Caillou the Road Builder/Caillou's Building Adventure/A House in the Sky
description: There's been a big storm and the playschool yard is littered with branches./When Daddy and Grandpa help a charity build a new home for a needy family, Caillou comes along./Mommy and Caillou go to visit an old friend of Mom's.

title: Caillou's Sleepover Guest/Games in the Park/The Sugar Shack/Winter Mystery/Caillou's Snowday
description: Leo is spending the night at Caillou's./Caillou is excited when Miss Martin takes him and his friends to the park for some special activities./When Caillou's family makes a springtime visit to Jonas' ranch, he takes them on a sleigh ride./The twins, Jason and Jeffrey, have come to play with Caillou in the snow./When Caillou, Rosie and Mom head to the big park, Caillou sees André.

title: Caillou and the Tooth Fairy/I Want to Grow Up/Caillou's Big Chill/Leo's Hamster
description: Caillou and Sarah are playing together when Caillou notices his friend wiggling her loose tooth back and forth./Caillou wants to be taller like his friend Andre and tries to think of a way to grow faster./Caillou is excited about the arrival of spring./Caillou loves Leo's pet hamster and would really like to have his own.

title: Snowflakes/Caillou Shoots! He Scores!/Caillou goes Tobogganing
description: Caillou eagerly awaits the first snowfall of winter, and imagines himself building the biggest snowman./Caillou wants to play hockey with Billy and the other big kids./Mommy can't find Caillou's toboggan for the playschool tobogganing trip.

title: Caillou's Water Park/Gone Fishing/The Water Goes 'Round/Caillou's Test Drive/A Very Good Swimmer!
description: Caillou learns that the best fun is made up and not bought and paid for./Caillou learns about patience when he goes fishing with Daddy and Grandpa at the pier./Grandma is watching Caillou for the day, and he wants her to play trucks with him./When their car breaks down, the family goes shopping for a new one./Caillou gets an introduction to what it means to be handicapped, when, at the pool, he meets Tammy.

title: Goes Camping/Learns to Skate/Gets Dressed/Daddy/Grows Carrots
description: Caillou hears about Daddy's first camping trip./Caillou has a hard time skating./Mom's doing the laundry./Mom and Rosie are out for the day. Caillou and Dad will spend the day together./Grandpa helps Mom make a vegetable garden.

title: New Kids on the Block/Caillou Goes to School/Caillou's Kitchen/Caillou's Sea Adventures
description: Walking by the empty lot at the end of the street, Caillou and Dad notice the real estate sign showing that it's been sold./When Sarah's school has a little sister or brother day, Sarah decides to invite Caillou./Mom is preparing a feast for guests and Caillou wants to help./It's another rainy day and Caillou decides to invite a friend over to play.

title: Learns to Drive/Big Friend/Colors/Mails a Letter/Learns to Swim
description: Caillou loves anything to do with cars./Caillou meets a new friend called André./Caillou visits Grandma's house./Mom is upset when the mailman only brings bills./Caillou goes to the swimming pool with his family and Daddy teaches him how to swim.

title: The Treasure Chest/A Camping We Will Go/Chopsticks/A Special Dog
description: Caillou is helping Mom clean out the attic./The family goes away for a weekend of camping in the woods./Caillou has dinner at Sarah's house and discovers new foods and a new way to eat them./Caillou and Mom meet a fascinating woman in the park.

title: Everyone's Best/Stronger Every Day/No More Training Wheels
description: When Clementine shows up with a swimming ribbon on her chest, Caillou really wants to have one too./When a new, longer set of monkey bars is installed at the park, Caillou is disappointed./With training wheels on his bike, Caillou is having trouble keeping up with Sarah.

title: Where's Gilbert?/Where I Saw it Last/Lost in the Jungle
description: Gilbert has gone missing and Caillou is very concerned./Caillou realizes that he has misplaced his new toy car./Caillou learns all about the jungle at playschool.

title: New Babysitter/Theme Park/School Bus/Sleeps Over/Hurts Himself
description: Mom and Dad are going out./Caillou and his family go to a theme park./Caillou doesn't go to school./It's the first time Caillou is going to spend the night away from his home./Poor Caillou! He's fallen off his bike and scraped his knee.

title: Plays Baby/Flies on a Plane/In the Bathtub/Goes Birdwatching/The Doll
description: Caillou thinks his sister Rosie is getting favorable treatment./It's Caillou's first flight./It's bathtime, and for Caillou that means trouble./Grandma always has the best surprises./Mom is putting on her makeup to go out with Dad.

title: Caillou's Gym Day/Our Rocket Ship/Caillou Helps Grandpa/The Backyard Bowlers/Caillou's Milk Run
description: Caillou gets a special invitation to go to André's gym class./Caillou and Leo are playing with their rocket ships in the park./On a winter day, Dad and Caillou go over to Grandpa's with their skates./When Caillou and Rosie stay at Grandma and Grandpa's house, Grandpa uses pop bottles and a rubber ball to create a kid's bowling alley./Caillou accidentally spills the rest of the milk before Rosie could get her cereal.

title: Birthday Present/Gilbert/Summer Goodnight/Scared of Dogs/The Zoo
description: It's Caillou's birthday and he's having a little party./Caillou has nobody to play with./Caillou just can't get to sleep./Caillou is scared by a stranger's dog./Caillou and his family go to the zoo.

title: Caillou Tries Karate/Just Like Daddy/Caillou's Safari/Cowboy Caillou
description: Leo comes over to play at Caillou's house./Daddy has a list of things to do around the house./Caillou wants to play with his animal cards but they have disappeared./Jonas, a friend of Dad's and a real cowboy, has invited the family to visit his ranch.

title: Shoo, Shoo Bird, Fly Away!/Caillou's Road Trip/Caillou and the Dragon
description: When birds keep eating the seeds in Mommy and Caillou's newly planted garden, they come up with the idea of making a scarecrow./One fine day the family is going on a car trip./There's a special visitor at Caillou's playschool - a boy named Alan who has Down Syndrome.

title: Caillou's Horn/The Mighty Oak/Get Well Mr. Hinkle/The Big Boat
description: When Sarah gives Caillou an old toy horn, Caillou wants to blow it everywhere./When Mr. Hinkle has a tree cut down, Caillou is afraid his swing tree is next!/When Caillou dresses up like a mailman to deliver Mr. Hinkle's misdirected mail, he finds out Mr. Hinkle is sick./Caillou and family go on a trip on Helen's boat, an old friend of Mom's.

title: Caillou's Big Slide/Caillou Walks a Dog/Caillou Watches Rosie/Caillou Gets Sick/Caillou's Phone Call
description: Caillou is playing in the park with Clementine./Grandma is looking after her friend's dog again./Mommy isn't feeling well./Caillou has a fever./Mom is busy on the phone all morning.

title: Caillou Helps Out/Caillou the Firefighter/Caillou to the Rescue
description: Rosie is teething and just can't seem to fall asleep./The Fire chief visits Caillou's playschool to teach the children about fire drills./A mischievous Rosie hides Caillou's cars between the cushions on the sofa.

title: Three's a Crowd/Get Well Soon/Shadow Play/A New Member of the Family
description: Caillou, Mom and Rosie go the park, where they join Leo and Clementine already playing in the sandbox./Caillou and Leo are having a great time playing spaceman when Leo trips and falls, hurting his foot./After supper one night, Caillou and Jason and Jeffrey decide to play hide and seek in the backyard./Caillou, Mom and Rosie are looking at pictures.

title: A Surprise for Mommy/Caillou Misses Sarah/T-Shirt Trouble/A Helping Hand
description: Dad gets a professional photo of Caillou and Rosie./Caillou's friend Sarah is going away on a trip for two whole weeks./Caillou's brand new T-shirt is ruined by grape juice./Caillou and Grandma, along with Rover the dog, spend a day at a retirement home.

title: Clowning Around/Read All About It/Mom for a Day/Caillou Plays Baseball
description: Caillou visits Grandma who shows him a book about clowns she got from the library./Caillou and Mom go to the library for story time./Caillou helps Daddy look after Rosie./When Caillou notices that Dad and Grandpa are captivated by a baseball game on TV, he wants to get in on the excitement.

title: A Sweet and Sour Day/Caillou's Puppet Show/Caillou's Collection
description: Caillou is helping Grandma water her flowers and fill the birdbath./Caillou and his friends Jason and Jeffrey make finger puppets at playschool and decide to put on a puppet show./In the park Caillou starts a new hobby - collecting rocks!

title: Where I Live/A Good Friend/Just Like Me/Just In Time/Mr. Fixit
description: When an invitation for Clementine's party accidentally ends up at Sarah's, Caillou learns the differences between the addresses of the two homes./When Leo forgets his brand new toy dinosaur in the park, Daddy and Caillou go looking for it./When Clementine tells Caillou how much she likes her older brother, Billy, to teach her things, Caillou sets out to teach something to Rosie./When Caillou's dawdling causes he, Mom and Rosie to be late going to the park, they end up missing Leo./When the washing machine needs fixing, Caillou ends up helping Bob the repairman.

title: Caillou Goes Caroling/A Playschool Party/Caillou's Christmas Eve
description: Caillou goes out caroling for the very first time with Mommy, Daddy, Rosie, Grandpa and Grandma./It's a very special day at playschool as they celebrate the many ways of celebrating the holiday season./It's finally Christmas Eve and Caillou just can't wait for nighttime.

title: Looks for Gilbert/Surprise Breakfast/Missing Sock/Goes to Work/Quarrel
description: Caillou is having a game of dinosaur hunter with Gilbert the cat./Caillou gets up early one morning./Caillou wants to wear his favorite socks, but one of them is missing./Caillou goes to work with Mom./Clementine comes over to play.

title: Show and Tell/Caillou the Magician/Caillou's Castle
description: Caillou has to decide on a nice surprise to bring to playschool for Show and Tell./Grandma shows Caillou a simple magic trick, which makes him decide to be a magician./Caillou wants to play castles and dragons, even though Gilbert isn't very keen on playing the dragon.

title: Caillou of the Antarctic/Deep Sea Caillou/Caillou in the Bayou
description: Caillou is playing with Jeffrey and Jason when he gets accidentally pushed down./There's a new girl named Lee Wun in playschool, but she's so shy she won't talk to anybody./The whole family is on the way to the beach but accidentally ends up on a trail through a swamp.
